    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Layout" kindref="compound">Layout</ref> controller manages layout invalidation and processing. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The layout controller is responsible for scheduling layout passes when layouts become invalid and processing them during the render loop. It integrates with the DALi adaptor system as a processor.</para>
<para>Each Window has its own <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1LayoutController" kindref="compound">LayoutController</ref> instance. The controller batches layout requests and processes them once per frame to optimize performance. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
